<HEADLINE> 'Soprano' Gets Into Club Free  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- When Jamie Lyn Sigler, better known as Meadow
Soprano in HBO's ''The Sopranos,'' showed up at a nightclub, she
got in free -- as did her boyfriend, brother and three others that
accompanied the actress.
</P>
<P>
   Hush owner Eddie Dean gladly let them in. But he says he felt
duped after Sigler and her boyfriend slipped out the backdoor a few
minutes later, leaving the others.
</P>
