Sanchez, president of the Democracy Movement; Oklahoma Gov. Frank
Keating, Roman Catholic Bishop William Curlin of Charlotte, N.C.,
Rabbi Marc Gellman of Melville, N.Y., and Southern Baptist
Convention President Rev. Paige Patterson.
