<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Cowboys' Emmitt Smith Gets Married  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   DALLAS (AP) -- Emmitt Smith, the Dallas Cowboys' star running
back, married actress Patricia Southall Lawrence on Saturday at the
First Baptist Church in downtown Dallas.
</P>
<P>
   Lawrence, who divorced actor-comedian Martin Lawrence in
September 1996, is a former Miss Virginia.
</P>
<P>
   Teammates Troy Aikman and Michael Irvin and Cowboys owner Jerry
Jones attended the ceremony. Aikman married former Cowboys public
relations staffer Rhonda Worthey on April 8.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER> AP-NY-04-22-00 2353 </TRAILER>
</DOC>
